<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>OK, can the administrator of this site please go through this page and weedle out all the crap and flames spouted by peeps here? I personally wanna know the best way to go about getting this robe and since I am only level 13, I have a LONG way to go until I can claim this Masterpiece for my own, which I WILL do at some point :) Just one point that I would like to raise for all you Carmine clad wizards out there: there isn't a HUGE amount of difference between CRoA and CR. Only 1 int point and I think 15 MP. That's a total of 25 mp at level 50+, you may aswell get a Skull of Jhen'tra :) Teeheehee. But still, I'd love to get this piece then I can up my lame strength some more, although by then I'll be buying weightless bags, but it's very annoying in my present situation! (ever tried to walk from Lesser Faydark ent to Kelethin newbie lift with an agility of 15?!? THAT was tiring :) Now before everyone loads up their flame catapults, please bare in mind that this is just my opinion. OK, so I may not think that a few ac and 25mp isn't much, but I'm the one who went apeshit when I upgraded from a SR Apprentice robe to a Gossimer robe :) Still, that extra 25mp may be enough for you to cast concussion and stop Cazic from aggroing on you when you try and Ice Comet him to death  and as I always say, every little bit helps :)</font></td></tr></table>
